<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shì fén ér bù huǐ de jīng jí, shén bì yǔ nǐ tóng zài.
 nǐ yào huǐ gǎi nǐ de xíng wèi, shén bì yǔ nǐ tóng zài.
 nǐ shì shén hū zhào de zhàn shì, shén bì yǔ nǐ tóng zài.
 nǐ yào tàng guò nà tiáo dà hé, shén bì yǔ nǐ tóng zài.
 nǐ yào zhǎo dào nǐ de xiōng dì, shén bì yǔ nǐ tóng zài.
 nǐ yào wèi shén de jiā jǐn zhōng, shén bì yǔ nǐ tóng zài.
 wǒ men de xīn yī tóng xiàng zhǔ chǎng kāi, shén bì yǔ wǒ men tóng zài.
 wú lùn zài tiān yá hǎi jiǎo chéng lǐ chéng wài, shén bì yǔ wǒ men tóng zài.</lyrics>
<title>shén bì yǔ nǐ tóng zài 迦南990</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
